{"tid":1440884,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)親親兩顆心 特務大臨演 曬撚氣1-2","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T20:50:59.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0edbdd1d0a2e213c948b27e7bac62a3cd0f470","tid":1440884,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:11:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPEuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=ecde054c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPEuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=7ae148d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPEuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=17da5348\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f9/Parenttrapposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff9%2FParenttrapposter.jpg&h=d717825e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/cb/The_Brothers_Grimsby_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fcb%2FThe_Brothers_Grimsby_Poster.jpg&h=064c27d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.荷莉&middot;帕克是一位11歲的小女孩，與父親在加州納帕縣的快樂的生活著，而父親尼克&middot;帕克是一位成功的葡萄園主人。荷莉的雙胞胎姊妹安妮&middot;詹姆士和母親住在倫敦，母親伊莉莎白&middot;詹姆士為一位婚紗設計師。這對姊妹完全不知道彼此的存在。<br />\n某年暑假，荷莉和安妮碰巧都參加了同一個夏令營。一開始，兩人視彼此為敵人，但兩人都有一些共同的特質：對草莓過敏，撲克牌高手，擅長惡作劇。某次他們在對對方惡作劇之後，輔導員將他們隔離且要求他們住在同一間寢室，他們便很快發現彼此的身世秘密。之後，他們計畫在夏令營結束時交換彼此的身份，去見他們無法相見的父母親..<br />\n<br />\n2.影片講述一名英國高級特工和一個足球流氓聯手完成任務的故事。高級間諜（馬克&middot;斯特朗飾）為了完成一項任務，他不得不同自己的足球流氓哥哥（薩莎&middot;拜倫&middot;科恩飾）攜手。 28年間，諾比一直在苦苦尋找他的弟弟。終於知道弟弟的下落之後，諾比興沖沖地前來相認，卻未料到弟弟的真實身份是一名英國軍情六處高級特工，並且正在執行一項事關整個世界生死存亡的緊急任務。令塞巴斯蒂安沒想到的是，當危險來臨時，唯一能夠幫助他脫困的就是這位他眼中全世界最蠢的傻蛋：自己的哥哥諾比<br />\n<br />\n3.蘿絲（Rose Da Silva）自小收養的女兒雪倫（Sharon Da Silva）患有夢遊症且多次提及小鎮『沉默之丘』。為尋求答案，蘿絲不顧丈夫克里斯席瓦（Christopher Da Silva）的反對於一天晚上帶著雪倫前往沉默之丘。在接近小鎮時二人被女警西碧兒（Cybil Bennett）追捕（因懷疑蘿絲企圖遺棄雪倫），蘿絲於驅車擺脫追捕時突然看見一女孩在路上出現，為閃避而撞上路邊失去知覺。蘿絲於醒來時發現雪倫竟已失蹤，白霧籠罩著一切，無數灰燼從天上持續地飄落。<br />\n<br />\n4.海瑟梅森和父親哈利梅森一直以來都在躲避不明力量的恐怖追殺。她18歲生日當晚，在夢魘纏身和父親神秘失蹤的詭譎情況下，海瑟發現自己原來從未瞭解「真正的自己」。隨著啟示錄的指引，她踏入了一個危機四伏、狂暴絕倫，可能令她永世不得脫身的邪惡世界&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n10 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPEuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=090f4840\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPEuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=bf3632fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7e875cfea291734aca50ab3f0bbbe9a45af9a7","tid":1440884,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/57/Silent_hill.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F57%2FSilent_hill.jpg&h=082b8fbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ffcd28339e4526553baa8b93abb99d103377183","tid":1440884,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f15e542b517f6a15da755eccb5a5c4f66c53f5","tid":1440884,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7571544bf76a1dead4cb98ef0298e50ea16ff3d6","tid":1440884,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1857fa7fe08afc05c2def9f5945391bfc869482f","tid":1440884,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48e0cab72306b8bac47cc03b0c7798f643f3e44","tid":1440884,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}